inputs.text: A portrait of a captivating vampire, chest-up. Her porcelain skin is flawless, with a subtle, ethereal glow that contrasts with her long, jet-black hair, cascading in soft waves around her face. Her sharp, angular features are defined by high cheekbones and a delicate, pointed chin, giving her an air of regal beauty. Her blood-red eyes shimmer with an almost hypnotic intensity, revealing an ancient hunger and the wisdom of centuries. Her lips, full and seductive, are slightly parted, showing the faintest hint of sharp fangs, ready to draw blood. She wears a dark, luxurious velvet gown that clings to her slender frame, adorned with intricate lace and silver filigree. A silver choker, set with a deep crimson gemstone, rests elegantly around her neck. The background is blurred, a shadowy, candle-lit gothic hall, where ancient stone walls and towering arches loom in the distance, creating an atmosphere of mystery and danger. Her presence exudes both elegance and an undeniable sense of deadly power, as if sheâ€™s been a ruler of the night for centuries.
